<help afk socials>

This command alerts those in your current room that you are
either stepping afk, or returning. It toggles the "afk" flag
and can be set with "toggle afk" as well as through the use
of the "afk" command. You will be marked as afk on the "who"
listing whenever you are afk.

Syntax: afk
Alternate Syntax: toggle afk

<color=red>
See Also:  toggle, socials
</color></help>
